Package saadadb.vo.translator

Class Summary
ConeSearchTranslator  
SiaTranslator Parser which translates a URL representing a HTTP GET request into a SaadaQL/s String This parser implements the 1.0 version of SIA which can be found at : http://www.ivoa.net/Documents/WD/SIA/sia-20040524.html The parser is compliant with the specification given above.
SsaTranslator  
VOQLTranslator Parser which translates a VOQL/x file into a SaadaQL/s String This parser implements the 1.01 version of ADQL which can be found at : http://www.ivoa.net/Documents/WD/ADQL/ADQL-20050624.doc All the constructs implemented by the SQLtoADQL Translator, found at http://openskyquery.net/AdqlTranslator/ADQLTrans.asmx?
VOTranslator Ancestor for the VO translators to SaadaQL/s
